         <t:abstract><t:p>Canons of Hippolytus exist in Gǝʿǝz exclusively as part of other works e. g. <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1544Gebrah">Gǝbra Ḥǝmāmāt</t:ref>. There is neither any independent
           occurrence of them nor do they exist, in whatever form, in their entirety.</t:p></t:abstract>
